antha]]''\n| Sai Ram\n| {{sort|Yeleti|[[Chandra Sekhar Yeleti]]}}\n| Telugu\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news|last=Sidhardhan|first=Sanjith|title=Mohanlal wraps up filming his Telugu movie|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/Mohanlal-wraps-up-filming-his-Telugu-movie/articleshow/50574492.cms|accessdate=25 February 2016|date=14 January 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225180814/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/Mohanlal-wraps-up-filming-his-Telugu-movie/articleshow/50574492.cms|archivedate=25 February 2016|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Janatha Garage]]''\n| Sathyam\n| {{sort|Siva|[[Koratala Siva]]}}\n| Telugu\n| \n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite news | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Mohanlal-is-NTRs-peddananna/articleshow/49934152.cms? | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219141527/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Mohanlal-is-NTRs-peddananna/articleshow/49934152.cms | archivedate=19 February 2016 | title=Mohanlal is NTR's peddananna | work=[[The Times of India]] | date=26 November 2016 | accessdate=1 December 2015 | last=Jonnalagedda | first=Pranita | url-status=live | df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n| 2019\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Kaappaan]]'' \n| Chandrakanth Varma\n| {{sort|Anand|[[K. V. Anand]]}}\n| Tamil\n| \n| \n|}\n<!-- Per WP:CRYSTAL & WP:NFF, DO NOT add films not yet in production.-->\n\n==Director==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"margin-right: 0;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Director\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{abbr|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n| 2021\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Barroz: Guardian of D'Gama's Treasure]]''\n| {{sort|Mohanlal|[[Mohanlal]]}}\n| Directorial Debut\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==Short films==